1International Institute for Applied Systems Analysis (IIASA), Laxenburg, Austria. 2Grantham Institute for Climate Change and the Environment, Imperial 
College London, London, UK. 3Centre for Environmental Policy, Imperial College London, London, UK. 4Institute for Integrated Energy Systems, University 
of Victoria, Victoria, British Columbia, Canada. 5Central European University (CEU), Budapest, Hungary. 6Tyndall Centre for Climate Change Research, 
University of East Anglia (UEA), Norwich, UK. 7Sustainable Energy Planning, Aalborg University, Aalborg, Denmark. 8Graz University of Technology, Graz, 
