Teleworking levels during the pandemic 
partially persist, leading to muted 
growth in the use of both light-duty 
vehicles (3%) and public transport 
(6%) compared with pre-pandemic 
structures. Surge in online retailing 
increases overall road freight 
activity. Aviation does not recover to 
