+2. Check whether the ENGAGE Scenario Explorer workspace is still accessible and whether the IIASA URL has moved from `ene` to `ece`.
+3. Inspect the GitHub figure script repository if a reproducibility-focused follow-up is needed.
+4. Decide whether this paper should seed a pattern page on activity-structure-intensity scenario design after the lab reaches the synthesis threshold.
+5. Compare this paper with future building-load, data-center-load, and H2-demand scenario papers to test how transferable the demand-persistence architecture is.
